sentences: Michael Collins Ajereh (born 26 November 1982), known professionally as Don Jazzy, is a Nigerian record producer, Brand Ambassador,  audio engineer, record executive, singer, entrepreneur, Influencer and Comedian.
Don Jazzy was  co-owner of the defunct Mo' Hits Records record label with Dbanj.
Don Jazzy was born Micheal Collins Ajereh in Umuahia, Abia State, on 26 November 1982, the son of Collins Enebeli Ajereh and Mrs Ajereh.
